庭/下一代<br />\n但問我生活辛苦係為左乜野?<br />\n我真係自己都答唔出<br />\n結果就係成日中途放棄<br />\n無毅力追求事業/金錢<br />\n以前覺得好憎社會垃圾廢中<br />\n而家先知其實自己同佢地距離好近<br />\n只要生活中行錯多一兩步就會變成佢地咁<br />\n但又唔知點樣阻止"},{"pid":"1d3ea5756960f8a7e4bb7bf8350cbed8e71f6e50","tid":2422884,"uid":149408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5325e4a3ef024f833f3ee0b640e3e36a20addeae","tid":2422884,"uid":80633,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0e70b53ea632d4bb2bb1ebd3e2c93dec83613d35","tid":2422884,"uid":149408,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T14:59:25.000Z","msg":"覺得做緊呢行冇前途 好想轉<br />\n但唔知可以轉乜<br />\n又唔想重新開始"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T16:09:55.000Z","msg":"一近三十好多人都係咁諗<br />\n工作熱誠無左，又見唔到前境<br />\n但我覺得有伴侶既話呢個問題會好解決d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T01:15:15.000Z","msg":"有伴侶....都係咁<br />\n變左一齊係到諗"},{"pid":"fee23610838e842ce20fd8e3dcda7ab12d35cae6","tid":2422884,"uid":349199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T01:18:00.000Z","msg":"一事無成，生活一塌糊塗"},{"pid":"ab34b54e77d5a33c2db6f743765bec91c0f2714c","tid":2422884,"uid":24883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T01:21:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />渾渾噩噩<br />\n完全唔知做嘜柒嘅人生"},{"pid":"842f9ee8a4e9618722b1a1eea79ee47270ca8744","tid":2422884,"uid":138089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T03:29:11.000Z","msg":"垃圾人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}